        • Serialized Fields

          • itemTable
            JTable itemTable
            The table for displaying items. This table is used to display the items in the shop inventory. Each row in the table represents a single item, and the columns represent the item's ID, name, creation date, update date, and expiration date.
          • scheduler
            ScheduledExecutorService scheduler
            The scheduled executor service for scheduled tasks. This executor service is used to schedule tasks to be executed at specific times or intervals.
          • searchField
            JTextField searchField
            The search field for filtering items. This field is used to search for specific items in the item table.
          • sortComboBox
            JComboBox<String> sortComboBox
            The sort combo box for sorting items. This combo box is used to sort the items in the item table based on the selected column.
          • sorter
            TableRowSorter<DefaultTableModel> sorter
            The row sorter for sorting items. This row sorter is used to sort the items in the item table based on the selected column.
          • tableModel
            DefaultTableModel tableModel
            The table model for the item table. This table model is used to manage the data displayed in the item table. It provides methods for adding, removing, and updating items in the table.
